<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US" class="h-full">
<head>
  <title>Webmention Endpoint</title>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="container">
    <h1>Webmention Endpoint</h1>

    {% set notice = craft.app.session.getFlash('notice') %}
    {% if notice %}
    <div class="callout notice">
      <p>
        {{ notice }}
      </p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% set error = craft.app.session.getFlash('error') %}
    {% if error %}
    <div class="callout error">
      <p>
        {{ error }}
      </p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <form action="" method="post" class="form">
      {{ csrfInput() }}
      <div class="field">
        <label for="source">Source URL</label>
        <input id="source" name="source" type="url">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="target">Target URL</label>
        <input id="target" name="target" type="text">
      </div>
        <button type="submit" class="button primary">Send Webmention</button>
    </form>
    <aside class="b-aside">
      <h4>About Webmention</h4>
      <p>Webmention is a modern alternative to pingback. If your site links back to content on my site, your site can send a Webmention for that URL and my site will – after a check – backlink to you.</p>
      <p>Webmention is part of the <a href="https://indiewebcamp.com/">IndieWeb</a>. You can read more about Webmention <a href="https://indiewebcamp.com/webmention">on the IndieWebCamp wiki.</a></p>
    </aside>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
